00:30.396 --> 00:33.166
♪♪♪♪

00:36.770 --> 00:38.805
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

00:44.210 --> 00:45.546
HELLO, HANNA.
HI.

00:45.546 --> 00:47.247
MRS. CRYER HERE?
MM‐HMM.

00:47.247 --> 00:48.314
NICE TO SEE YOU.

00:48.314 --> 00:49.415
NICE TO SEE YOU.

00:51.017 --> 00:52.719
HOLD ON,
I'LL GO GET HER.

00:52.719 --> 00:54.387
OKAY.

00:54.387 --> 00:56.489
♪♪♪♪

00:57.524 --> 00:59.225
HEY.

00:59.225 --> 01:00.927
HEY.

01:00.927 --> 01:03.403
MR. BOWMAN'S HERE
TO SEE YOU.

01:03.403 --> 01:05.138
WHAT IS HE DOING HERE?

01:05.138 --> 01:07.073
