TO HIM.

01:07.073 --> 01:08.575
OKAY.
SEE YOU.

01:08.575 --> 01:10.544
NO.
WAIT, NO.

01:10.544 --> 01:12.245
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

01:12.245 --> 01:13.580
HAVE SOME TEA.

01:13.580 --> 01:19.119
OKAY.

01:20.587 --> 01:23.356
LLOYD,
I JUST TALKED TO YOU.

01:23.356 --> 01:24.658
YES, I KNOW.

01:24.658 --> 01:26.593
WELL,
WHAT IS IT?

01:26.593 --> 01:28.328
WE HAVE AN ISSUE.

01:28.328 --> 01:29.429
WHAT KIND OF ISSUE?

01:29.429 --> 01:30.531
