01:30.531 --> 01:32.999
TO GET THEM TO SEND BACK
THE WIRE TRANSFER.

01:32.999 --> 01:34.735
WHY NOT?

01:34.735 --> 01:36.837
THE BANK PRESIDENT
CALLED THE D. A.

01:36.837 --> 01:38.471
AND WHY
WOULD HE DO THAT?

01:38.471 --> 01:41.407
WELL, APPARENTLY, SHE TOLD HIM
THAT IF ANYONE CALLED

01:41.407 --> 01:44.177
AND TRIED TO ADJUST THE ACCOUNTS
TO CONTACT HER.

01:44.177 --> 01:48.448
NOW SHE'S GOTTEN A JUDGE
TO OVERRULE YOUR JUDGE'S RULING.

01:48.448 --> 01:49.449
WHAT?

01:49.449 --> 01:51.818
NOW THEY WON'T
SEND US THE MONEY.

01:51.818 --> 01:53.687
ARE YOU SERIOUS?

01:53.687 --> 01:54.788
MM‐HMM.

01:54.788 --> 01:56.990
WYATT STILL HAS THE MONEY
IN HIS NAME.

01:56.990 --> 01:58.925
LLOYD!
THE JUDGE STOPPED IT.

01:58.925 --> 02:00.834
I'M SORRY.

02:00.834 --> 02:02.468
WHAT IS SHE
TRYING TO DO?

02:02.468 --> 02:03.704
KILL HIM?

02:03.704 --> 02:05.338
I ‐‐ I DON'T KNOW.

02:05.338 --> 02:06.940
I'M ‐‐ I'M SORRY.

02:08.474 --> 02:09.475
[ SIGHS ]

02:09.475 --> 02:11.277
I'LL DEAL WITH IT.
IT'S OKAY.

02:11.277 --> 02:13.714
WELL, WHAT WOULD YOU
LIKE ME TO DO?

02:13.714 --> 02:15.448
NOTHING.
ARE YOU SURE?

02:15.448 --> 02:18.051
YES, JUST ‐‐
JUST GO BACK TO THE BANK.

02:18.051 --> 02:20.654
IF THE COURTS
WILL NOT PROTECT MY SON,

02:20.654 --> 02:23.624
THEN IT LOOKS LIKE
I'M GONNA HAVE TO.

02:23.624 --> 02:25.726
WELL, PLEASE LET ME KNOW
IF THERE'S ANYTHING I CAN DO.

02:25.726 --> 02:28.762
WELL, YOU'VE DONE A LOT ALREADY,
AND I APPRECIATE IT.

02:28.762 --> 02:29.963
THANK YOU.
OKAY.

02:29.963 --> 02:32.799
I'M SORRY
I'VE RUINED YOUR DAY.

02:32.799 --> 02:35.001
NO.

02:35.001 --> 02:36.169
NO...

02:36.169 --> 02:40.006
BUT YOU'RE ABOUT TO RUIN
SOMEBODY'S DAY.

02:40.006 --> 02:42.175
BUT NOT MINE.

