KEEP IT.

03:30.564 --> 03:32.165
MRS. CRYER ‐‐

03:32.165 --> 03:33.366
YOU NEED A CAR.

03:33.366 --> 03:35.168
I'M FINE.

03:35.168 --> 03:36.837
♪♪♪♪

03:36.837 --> 03:38.739
KEEP IT.

03:42.543 --> 03:43.777
HERE.

03:43.777 --> 03:44.878
WHAT IS THAT?

03:44.878 --> 03:46.379
THE TITLE.

03:46.379 --> 03:47.413
MRS. CRYER.

03:47.413 --> 03:49.382
AND IT ALREADY
HAS YOUR NAME ON IT

03:49.382 --> 03:51.084
BECAUSE I KNEW
YOU WOULD SAY NO.

03:51.084 --> 03:54.855
AND THE GIFT TAX
IS PAID FOR.

03:54.855 --> 03:56.222
SO THERE.

03:56.222 --> 03:58.625
♪♪♪♪

