STILL THE CASE?

04:11.912 --> 04:14.280
I'M SORRY.

04:14.280 --> 04:16.783
OKAY.

04:16.783 --> 04:19.285
OKAY.

04:19.285 --> 04:22.455
BUT I REALLY DO
APPRECIATE THIS.

04:22.455 --> 04:23.924
I KNOW YOU DO.

04:23.924 --> 04:26.760
YOU'VE ALWAYS BEEN THERE
FOR ME, HANNA.

04:26.760 --> 04:27.928
OH.

04:27.928 --> 04:29.763
THERE'S AN OLD...

04:29.763 --> 04:32.833
CAR SEAT IN THE ATTIC ‐‐
SOMEWHERE.

04:32.833 --> 04:34.433
