04:38.271 --> 04:39.372
[ CHUCKLES ]

04:39.372 --> 04:41.407
HE'S BIG ENOUGH
TO RIDE IN THE BACK SEAT.

04:41.407 --> 04:43.777
GOOD.

04:43.777 --> 04:45.612
♪♪♪♪

04:45.612 --> 04:47.247
WELL...

04:47.247 --> 04:49.683
SEE YOU SOON.

04:49.683 --> 04:52.085
WILL YOU COME VISIT ME,
HANNA?

04:52.085 --> 04:54.655
WHY YOU ACT LIKE
YOU'RE GOING SOMEWHERE?

04:54.655 --> 04:58.258
MIGHT BE
TALKING ABOUT IT.

04:58.258 --> 05:00.126
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

05:00.126 --> 05:02.836
YES.

05:02.836 --> 05:04.470
YOU SURE?

05:04.470 --> 05:07.508
OH. YES.

05:08.842 --> 05:11.144
ARE YOU GOING BACK
TO SEE WYATT TODAY?

05:11.144 --> 05:13.947
MNH‐MNH.

05:13.947 --> 05:15.682
NO.

05:15.682 --> 05:17.851
OKAY.

05:17.851 --> 05:20.120
♪♪♪♪

05:20.120 --> 05:22.455
I'LL SEE YOU
WHEN YOU COME VISIT ME.

05:22.455 --> 05:24.791
OKAY,
I'LL SEE YOU LATER.

05:24.791 --> 05:27.460
LET'S SEE IF I CAN
PEEL THEM AWAY FROM THESE TOYS.

05:27.460 --> 05:29.830
[ CHUCKLES ]

05:29.830 --> 05:35.368
