<i>HI, THIS IS CANDACE.</i>

05:55.656 --> 05:58.525
YOU KNOW WHAT TO DO.
[ SIGHS ]

05:58.525 --> 06:00.226
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

06:00.226 --> 06:02.235
Jeffery: Yes?
DID SHE ANSWER?

06:02.235 --> 06:04.237
NO.
Keep trying.

06:04.237 --> 06:05.506
I AM, I AM.

06:05.506 --> 06:08.241
JEFFERY,
IS THERE SOMETHING IN THERE?

06:08.241 --> 06:09.275
[ SIGHS ]

