MAYBE I CAN HELP YOU.

06:16.550 --> 06:18.785
HOW?
HOW CAN YOU?

06:18.785 --> 06:19.886
I DON'T KNOW.

06:19.886 --> 06:21.888
IS THERE AN AREA
WHERE I CAN SEARCH, MAYBE?

06:23.423 --> 06:26.359
I DON'T KNOW,
I DON'T KNOW.

06:26.359 --> 06:29.162
JEFFERY,
LET ME HELP YOU.

06:29.162 --> 06:31.164
WHERE CAN I SEARCH?

06:32.699 --> 06:33.767
BACKYARD.

06:33.767 --> 06:36.402
SEARCH JUST
THE BACKYARD.

06:36.402 --> 06:38.805
OKAY,
WHERE IN THE BACKYARD?

06:38.805 --> 06:40.373
[ SIGHS ]

06:40.373 --> 06:42.475
BY THE GARDEN.

06:42.475 --> 06:44.210
OKAY.

06:44.210 --> 06:45.712
UM...

06:45.712 --> 06:47.548
JUSTIN?

06:47.548 --> 06:48.749
YEAH?

06:48.749 --> 06:51.251
If there are
keys found...

06:51.251 --> 06:52.553
YEAH?

06:52.553 --> 06:54.955
YOU NEED
TO FIND THEM.

06:54.955 --> 06:57.457
OKAY,
DO YOU UNDERSTAND?

06:57.457 --> 06:59.593
OKAY.

06:59.593 --> 07:00.794
[ SIGHS ]

07:00.794 --> 07:02.135
THANK YOU, THANK YOU,
THANK YOU, THANK YOU.

07:02.135 --> 07:04.137
MY BOSS IS COMING.
I GOT TO GO.

07:04.137 --> 07:06.006
Keep trying her.

07:06.006 --> 07:09.042
OKAY, OKAY, OKAY.
THANKS.

07:09.042 --> 07:10.276
[ SIGHS ]

07:10.276 --> 07:14.648
[ CHATTER ]

07:17.651 --> 07:19.520
Woman:
UH, YOUNG LADY?!

07:19.520 --> 07:21.855
JUST STEP AWAY
FROM THE FENCE.

07:21.855 --> 07:23.790
STEP AWAY
FROM THE FENCE.

07:23.790 --> 07:26.292
MAN, OLD BITCH,
STOP TALKING TO ME!

07:26.292 --> 07:27.594
DAMN!

07:27.594 --> 07:30.230
OKAY,
LET'S GO IN.

07:31.264 --> 07:34.300
POLICE,
SEARCH WARRANT!

07:34.300 --> 07:37.470
♪♪♪♪

07:41.775 --> 07:44.811
♪♪♪♪

07:44.811 --> 07:46.446
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATES ]

07:46.446 --> 07:47.480
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

07:47.480 --> 07:48.915
CANDACE, WHERE THE HELL
HAVE YOU BEEN?

07:48.915 --> 07:50.316
YOU CHEATING ON ME?

07:50.316 --> 07:51.384
WHAT?

07:51.384 --> 07:53.419
