I'M NOT ASKING FOR ME.

08:03.504 --> 08:05.906
LOOK,
I'M NOT THERE.

08:05.906 --> 08:08.642
[ SIGHS ]

08:08.642 --> 08:10.677
YOU SHOULD BE.

08:10.677 --> 08:13.046
JEFFERY: Melissa?

08:13.046 --> 08:14.748
HELLO, SON.

08:14.748 --> 08:17.150
MOM.

08:17.150 --> 08:18.351
WHERE ARE YOU?

08:18.351 --> 08:20.120
I'm out.
OUT WHERE?

08:20.120 --> 08:23.123
PICKING UP A SUIT
FOR TONIGHT.

08:23.123 --> 08:25.592
WE HAVE STAFF
FOR THAT, DEAR.

08:25.592 --> 08:29.530
WELL,
I NEEDED TO GET SOME AIR.

08:29.530 --> 08:32.132
BUT YOU CAN'T
GET AIR THERE.

08:32.132 --> 08:34.635
WELL,
I'M TRYING TO.

08:34.635 --> 08:37.838
MELISSA,
EXCUSE ME, PLEASE.

08:40.140 --> 08:41.508
JEFFERY: Mom?

08:41.508 --> 08:44.444
GET YOUR ASS HOME.
RIGHT NOW.

08:44.444 --> 08:46.613
MOM.

08:46.613 --> 08:47.914
JEFFERY,
DO YOU UNDERSTAND

08:47.914 --> 08:49.983
THAT WE HAVE A DINNER PARTY
PLANNED FOR TONIGHT

08:49.983 --> 08:52.953
