MELISSA'S PARENTS BEFORE THEN?

08:52.953 --> 08:55.321
YOU NEED TO ASK HER FATHER
FOR HER HAND IN MARRIAGE,

08:55.321 --> 08:58.324
AND YOU NEED
TO LOOK PRESENTABLE DOING IT.

08:58.324 --> 09:01.868
NOW, STOP WASTING
YOUR TIME <i>THERE</i> AND GET <i>HERE.</i>

09:01.868 --> 09:03.003
Now.

09:03.003 --> 09:04.538
Are we clear?

09:04.538 --> 09:07.741
WHY THE HELL
WOULD I DO THAT?

09:07.741 --> 09:08.842
WHAT?

09:08.842 --> 09:10.476
You heard me.

09:10.476 --> 09:13.547
YOU HAVE
NO MORE CARDS TO PLAY.

09:13.547 --> 09:15.415
WHAT?

09:15.415 --> 09:18.084
SO I'M NOT COMING.

09:18.084 --> 09:21.154
JEFFERY, DO YOU WANT ME
TO CALL THE D. A.?

09:21.154 --> 09:22.789
[ CHUCKLES ]

09:22.789 --> 09:24.825
YOU ALREADY DID.

09:24.825 --> 09:27.427
[ SCOFFS ] OKAY.

09:27.427 --> 09:28.695
OH...

09:28.695 --> 09:30.230
YOU ‐‐
YOU DON'T KNOW?

09:30.230 --> 09:31.998
What are you
talking about?

