ARE SERVING A SEARCH WARRANT

09:34.367 --> 09:37.504
AT CANDACE'S HOUSE
RIGHT NOW.

09:37.504 --> 09:39.973
And you didn't know?

09:39.973 --> 09:42.609
NO,
I DIDN'T KNOW.

09:42.609 --> 09:45.579
WELL,
THEY ARE.

09:45.579 --> 09:48.715
WELL, THEN,
YOU NEED TO GET HOME NOW.

09:48.715 --> 09:51.217
WHY THE HELL
WOULD I DO THAT, MOM?

09:51.217 --> 09:53.554
YOU HAVE
NO MORE CARDS TO PLAY.

09:53.554 --> 09:56.022
