YOUR ONLY HOPE.

10:00.801 --> 10:02.002
HMM.

10:02.002 --> 10:03.904
YOU KNOW WHAT?

10:03.904 --> 10:07.407
I'M GONNA TAKE
MY CHANCES.

10:07.407 --> 10:10.010
GET HOME, JEFFERY,
NOW.

10:11.044 --> 10:13.079
GO TO HELL,
VERONICA.

10:13.079 --> 10:14.681
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

10:14.681 --> 10:18.318
♪♪♪♪

10:31.832 --> 10:34.367
YOU'RE NOT GONNA TALK
TO ME, BENNY?

10:34.367 --> 10:39.740
♪♪♪♪

10:42.543 --> 10:45.746
I'M GONNA GET
THE MONEY BACK, B.

10:46.780 --> 10:49.215
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

10:49.215 --> 10:51.518
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

10:52.052 --> 10:54.054
JEFFERY,
I CAN'T TALK RIGHT NOW.

10:54.054 --> 10:55.689
I'M TURNING OFF
MY PHONE.

10:55.689 --> 10:56.857
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

10:56.857 --> 11:00.100
♪♪♪♪

11:06.873 --> 11:10.076
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

11:10.076 --> 11:16.116
♪♪♪♪

11:17.884 --> 11:19.119
HI.

11:19.119 --> 11:20.787
HELLO.

11:20.787 --> 11:22.088
YOU'RE PROMPT.

11:22.088 --> 11:24.390
WELL, I TRY TO BE.
HMM.

11:25.425 --> 11:27.561
SO YOU WANT
TO KNOW MY NAME?

11:27.561 --> 11:29.996
YES, PLEASE.

11:29.996 --> 11:32.265
I'M ERICA.

11:32.265 --> 11:33.433
RIGHT.

11:33.433 --> 11:34.935
PLEASURE TO MEET YOU,
ERICA.

11:34.935 --> 11:36.169
I'M DAVID.

11:36.169 --> 11:37.170
HMM.

11:37.170 --> 11:38.471
BUT YOU ALREADY
KNOW THAT.

11:38.471 --> 11:39.673
YES, I DO.

11:39.673 --> 11:40.841
RIGHT. SO...

11:40.841 --> 11:43.910
SHALL I TAKE YOU BACK
TO THE HOTEL?

11:43.910 --> 11:45.512
NO.

11:45.512 --> 11:46.980
NO?
NO.

11:46.980 --> 11:50.250
WHERE WOULD YOU
LIKE TO GO?

11:50.250 --> 11:52.352
WELL, THERE'S THIS
DIVE OF A DINER

11:52.352 --> 11:54.888
