THAT I LOVE.

11:54.888 --> 11:56.923
IT HAS
REAL SOUL FOOD.

11:56.923 --> 11:58.324
REAL SOUL FOOD?

11:58.324 --> 11:59.760
MM‐HMM.
A‐HA.

11:59.760 --> 12:02.536
WHEN'S THE LAST TIME
