IN THAT CASE,
IT'S BEEN QUITE A WHILE.

12:11.477 --> 12:13.614
YOU SEE, MY WIFE NEVER ‐‐
AH, MISTAKE NUMBER THREE.

12:13.614 --> 12:15.949
AH. RIGHT.

12:15.949 --> 12:17.317
DON'T TALK ABOUT THE EX.
NO EX TALK.

12:17.317 --> 12:18.384
YEAH.
OKAY.

12:18.384 --> 12:20.020
[ SIGHS ]

12:20.020 --> 12:21.287
COME ON.

12:21.287 --> 12:23.456
SO, WHAT ‐‐
NOT TAKING THE CAR?

12:23.456 --> 12:25.191
NO,
WE'RE WALKING.

12:25.191 --> 12:27.127
AND, UM...

12:27.127 --> 12:29.830
LOSE THE TIE
AND ‐‐ AND THE STUFFINESS.

12:29.830 --> 12:31.464
AND THE STUFFI‐‐
OH.

12:31.464 --> 12:33.333
[ LAUGHS ]
TIE AND STUFFINESS.

12:33.333 --> 12:34.367
MM‐HMM.
GONE.

12:34.367 --> 12:36.169
COME ON,
LET'S GO.

12:36.169 --> 12:37.470
HO‐HOLD ON.

12:37.470 --> 12:40.541
LET ME
OPEN THE DOOR FOR YOU.

12:42.042 --> 12:43.443
GOT YOU.

12:51.985 --> 12:54.721
LET'S GO.

12:56.089 --> 12:58.725
I, UH...

12:58.725 --> 13:01.401
