GET ENGAGED TO MELISSA.

13:09.743 --> 13:12.112
ANYWAY, UM...

13:12.112 --> 13:15.916
I MAY BE AWAY
WHEN YOU GET OUT OF HERE.

13:17.350 --> 13:21.087
BUT I NEED YOU TO KNOW
THAT I LOVE YOU, WYATT.

13:24.224 --> 13:27.728
I'VE ALWAYS LOVED YOU.

13:27.728 --> 13:30.697
