27:04.470 --> 27:07.007
I'M IN BUSINESS
WITH THE MOB.

27:07.007 --> 27:08.274
NO, YOU'RE IN BUSINESS
WITH ME.

27:08.274 --> 27:10.811
THAT'S HOW YOU GOT THESE PHONES
BACK ON, HUH?

27:10.811 --> 27:12.646
NO, NO, THAT'S HOW I GOT THEM
TO BACK OFF.

27:12.646 --> 27:13.947
YOU SEE,
IT'S GOT IT'S UPS.

27:13.947 --> 27:16.016
YEAH,
UNTIL IT HAS ITS DOWNS.

27:16.016 --> 27:17.317
THAT DOESN'T MATTER.
I'M NOT IN IT, DUDE.

27:17.317 --> 27:18.719
I'M WITH YOU.

27:18.719 --> 27:21.354
YEAH,
BUT YOU SET WAR UP.

27:21.354 --> 27:23.256
'CAUSE HE WAS GONNA
KILL YOU, MAN.

27:23.256 --> 27:26.459
HE WAS GONNA POP YOU,
THAT DUDE.

27:26.459 --> 27:28.161
YOU HAVE MY BACK?

27:28.161 --> 27:29.462
AND HERS.

27:29.462 --> 27:30.531
WELL...

27:30.531 --> 27:32.498
I HATE TO BREAK IT TO YOU
LIKE THIS,

27:32.498 --> 27:34.500
BUT SHE MORTGAGED
THIS PLACE.

27:34.500 --> 27:37.137
WHAT?
YEAH, AND MY HOUSE.

27:37.137 --> 27:39.573
IF I DON'T GOT $2 MILLION
IN THE BANK IN 24 HOURS,

27:39.573 --> 27:41.374
[SNAPS FINGERS]
THIS PLACE IS GONE.

27:41.374 --> 27:43.644
♪♪♪♪

27:43.644 --> 27:45.178
THIS IS MY DREAM,
MAN.

27:45.178 --> 27:46.780
YOU KNOW?
AND NOW LOOK.

27:46.780 --> 27:47.814
YEAH.

27:47.814 --> 27:51.017
A JOKE.

27:51.017 --> 27:52.152
[ SIGHS ]

27:52.152 --> 27:53.854
YO,
I CAN GET IT.

27:54.888 --> 27:56.990
OH, HELL NO.

27:56.990 --> 27:59.459
NO WAY.
NO.

27:59.459 --> 28:00.493
YEAH, I KNOW.

28:00.493 --> 28:03.036
'CAUSE THEN WE WOULD
OWE THEM MONEY AND...

28:03.036 --> 28:04.738
YEAH,
YOU'RE DAMN RIGHT.

28:04.738 --> 28:06.873
LISTEN, I'D GIVE IT ALL UP FIRST
BEFORE I LET THAT HAPPEN.

28:06.873 --> 28:08.074
YEAH, YEAH, THAT'S SMART.
NO.

28:08.074 --> 28:09.342
NO, YOU'RE RIGHT,
THAT'S SMART.

28:09.342 --> 28:11.878
'CAUSE ‐‐ 'CAUSE THEM AND MONEY,
OOH, MAN.

28:11.878 --> 28:13.747
THAT'S NOT GOOD
FOR ANYBODY.

28:13.747 --> 28:15.649
'CAUSE THAT MONEY
FROM MY FAMILY,

28:15.649 --> 28:16.717
AIN'T NOBODY SAFE.

28:16.717 --> 28:19.152
NOT YOUR MAMA,
NOT YOUR NEPHEW ‐‐ NOBODY.

28:19.152 --> 28:21.755
YOU FEEL ME?
ALL RIGHT?

28:21.755 --> 28:24.057
MY UNCLES, MAN, THEY DON'T PLAY.
YOU FEEL ME?

28:24.057 --> 28:25.592
LIKE,
I'VE SEEN IT.

28:25.592 --> 28:27.193
YEAH,
I CAN IMAGINE.

28:27.193 --> 28:28.729
THAT'S WHY I WENT OUT.

28:31.765 --> 28:33.199
SO WHAT ARE
WE GONNA DO NOW?

28:33.199 --> 28:36.036
[ SIGHS ]

28:36.036 --> 28:38.505
WELL,
THE HELL IF I KNOW, MAN.

28:38.505 --> 28:41.207
I GUESS WE JUST
START ALL OVER, RIGHT?

28:41.207 --> 28:43.777
♪♪♪♪

28:43.777 --> 28:46.580
[ SIGHS ]

28:54.555 --> 28:57.090
[ GROANS ]

28:59.225 --> 29:02.402
YEAH. YES, SIR.
OH.

29:02.402 --> 29:04.270
THE BOY'S
GOT SOME TASTE!

29:04.270 --> 29:05.471
BEEN SAVING THIS.

29:05.471 --> 29:07.273
WELL,
THAT'S NICE, MAN.

29:09.576 --> 29:10.811
HERE.
ALL RIGHT.

29:10.811 --> 29:13.413
LET'S GET IT GOING.
WE GOT SOME CUPS, RIGHT?

29:13.413 --> 29:15.248
I'M GONNA POP
THESE BOTTLES.

29:15.248 --> 29:16.282
WHOO!

29:16.282 --> 29:18.151
AT LEAST WE DID IT
FOR A MINUTE, RIGHT?

29:18.151 --> 29:19.920
YEAH,
FOR A MINUTE, RIGHT?

29:19.920 --> 29:21.121
ALL RIGHT.
HEY.

29:21.121 --> 29:22.188
KEEPING IT CLASSY,
RIGHT?

29:22.188 --> 29:23.790
THAT'S WHAT I'M TRYING TO SAY,
YEAH, HEY.

29:23.790 --> 29:24.958
HOW WE DO
AT BENNY'S TOWING.

29:24.958 --> 29:26.326
ALL THE WAY,
YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN?

29:26.326 --> 29:28.862
LET'S DO IT.

29:28.862 --> 29:30.330
YEAH!

29:30.330 --> 29:32.132
MY MAN!

29:32.132 --> 29:33.466
♪♪♪♪

29:33.466 --> 29:35.468
AFTER YOU,
AFTER YOU, SIR.

29:35.468 --> 29:36.603
THAT'S FOR YOU.

29:36.603 --> 29:38.071
THERE YOU GO.
OH, YOU THE MAN.

29:38.071 --> 29:39.272
OH.

29:39.272 --> 29:40.974
I DON'T KNOW WHERE WE GONNA GO
FROM HERE, BUT...

29:40.974 --> 29:41.975
NO.

29:41.975 --> 29:43.343
WE GO TO THE FUTURE,
MAN.

29:43.343 --> 29:44.611
WE TOAST
TO THE FUTURE.

29:44.611 --> 29:46.012
YEAH?

29:46.012 --> 29:47.047
TO BENNY'S TOWING.

29:47.047 --> 29:48.649
THAT'S WHAT
IT'S ALL ABOUT.

29:48.649 --> 29:51.084
BOTTOMS UP,
MAN.

29:51.084 --> 29:52.152
[ SIGHS ]

29:52.152 --> 29:54.120
YEAH, MAN.
MM‐HMM.

30:01.668 --> 30:04.705
[ DOORKNOB RATTLING ]

30:27.594 --> 30:30.631
[ TAPPING ]

30:34.334 --> 30:37.938
♪♪♪♪

30:46.613 --> 30:48.715
WHERE IS MY MONEY?

30:48.715 --> 30:50.183
♪♪♪♪

30:50.183 --> 30:51.484
HMM?

30:51.484 --> 30:52.753
HUH?

30:52.753 --> 30:54.187
HUH?!

30:54.187 --> 30:55.989
TAKE MY MONEY?!

30:55.989 --> 30:57.524
WHERE IS IT?

30:57.524 --> 30:59.826
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

30:59.826 --> 31:02.068
JENNIFER SALLISON.

31:02.068 --> 31:03.870
HI, JENNIFER.
Yes?

31:03.870 --> 31:05.872
IT'S VERONICA HARRINGTON.

31:05.872 --> 31:07.974
HOW ARE YOU?

31:07.974 --> 31:09.643
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

31:09.643 --> 31:12.713
KATHERYN CRYER CALLED ME,
VERY UPSET.

31:12.713 --> 31:14.581
WHAT ELSE IS NEW?

31:14.581 --> 31:17.518
SHE WOULD LIKE FOR ME
TO NEGOTIATE WITH YOU.

31:17.518 --> 31:18.819
WHY?

31:18.819 --> 31:21.087
SHE WOULD LIKE FOR ME
TO FIND A WAY TO SPEAK WITH YOU.

31:21.087 --> 31:23.256
LOOK, THERE'S NO DEALING HERE
WITH JIM.

31:23.256 --> 31:24.825
THIS ISN'T ABOUT JIM.

31:24.825 --> 31:26.359
THIS IS ABOUT WYATT.

31:26.359 --> 31:28.161
HIM, EITHER.

31:28.161 --> 31:29.596
HIS INHERITANCE.

31:29.596 --> 31:33.199
SHE WOULD LIKE
TO MEET WITH YOU PERSONALLY.

31:33.199 --> 31:34.535
WHY?

31:34.535 --> 31:35.969
Look,
I know that you gave him

31:35.969 --> 31:37.437
full access
to his inheritance,

31:37.437 --> 31:39.239
BUT THE WOMAN
IS IN PAIN.

31:39.239 --> 31:41.542
CAN WE AT LEAST MEET
TO DISCUSS HIM

31:41.542 --> 31:44.377
NOT HAVING TOTAL ACCESS
TO IT,

31:44.377 --> 31:46.279
MAYBE PARTIAL ACCESS?

31:46.279 --> 31:47.848
Isn't that fair?

31:47.848 --> 31:49.683
I GUESS THAT'S FAIR.

31:49.683 --> 31:52.352
OKAY,
SO, THE CRYER HOUSE,

31:52.352 --> 31:53.887
LET'S SAY 6:00.

31:53.887 --> 31:56.222
OKAY.
BUT, VERONICA?

31:56.222 --> 31:57.457
Yes.

31:57.457 --> 32:02.135
IF SHE THREATENS ME AGAIN,
I'M GONNA HAVE HER ARRESTED.

32:02.135 --> 32:03.169
YOU CAN.

32:03.169 --> 32:05.305
THIS ISN'T ABOUT THAT.

32:05.305 --> 32:07.774
THIS IS
ABOUT HER SON.

32:07.774 --> 32:08.909
OKAY.

32:08.909 --> 32:11.678
I'LL SEE YOU THERE.

32:11.678 --> 32:13.379
Thank you.

32:13.379 --> 32:14.447
BYE.

32:16.116 --> 32:22.623
♪♪♪♪

32:38.972 --> 32:40.774
UNCLE BENNY!

32:40.774 --> 32:42.275
HEY, MAN!

32:42.275 --> 32:44.444
IS THIS YOUR HOUSE?

32:44.444 --> 32:45.779
YEAH, MAN.

32:45.779 --> 32:47.113
CAN I STAY HERE?

32:47.113 --> 32:48.314
YEAH.

32:48.314 --> 32:50.450
I CAN STAY HERE
AS LONG AS I WANT TO?

32:50.450 --> 32:51.985
♪♪♪♪

32:51.985 --> 32:53.854
YEAH.

32:53.854 --> 32:55.321
I LIKE IT.

32:55.321 --> 32:56.389
GOOD.

32:56.389 --> 33:00.426
I DON'T KNOW
HOW YOU DID IT.

33:00.426 --> 33:03.136
YEAH.
WHOSE CAR?

33:03.136 --> 33:04.270
HMM.

33:04.270 --> 33:05.872
BELIEVE IT OR NOT,
MY BOSS GAVE IT TO ME.

33:05.872 --> 33:07.207
YEAH,
YOUR BOSS?

33:07.207 --> 33:09.275
WELL, EX‐BOSS.

33:09.275 --> 33:11.978
OKAY.

33:11.978 --> 33:13.847
NO, NO, NO.

33:13.847 --> 33:16.282
WHAT'S WRONG?

33:16.282 --> 33:18.018
NOTHING.

33:18.018 --> 33:20.987
Q,
GO BACK UPSTAIRS

33:20.987 --> 33:24.691
AND FINISH READING
THAT BOOK I WAS READING TO YOU.

33:33.166 --> 33:35.268
WHAT'S GOING ON?

33:36.803 --> 33:39.172
YOU'RE JUST GONNA SAY,
"I TOLD YOU SO."

33:39.172 --> 33:40.941
WHAT IS IT?

33:42.475 --> 33:45.145
MOM...

33:45.145 --> 33:47.714
WHAT DID SHE DO?

33:47.714 --> 33:50.517
SHE...

33:50.517 --> 33:52.185
TELL ME.

33:54.220 --> 33:57.457
SHE MORTGAGED
MY HOUSE.

33:57.457 --> 33:59.726
AND THE TOW YARD.

34:02.769 --> 34:07.207
LORD JESUS.

34:07.207 --> 34:09.610
AND SHE FORGED
MY SIGNATURE.

34:09.610 --> 34:11.845
♪♪♪♪

34:11.845 --> 34:13.379
BANK SAYS
IF THEY DON'T GET THE MONEY

34:13.379 --> 34:16.382
BY 5:00 TOMORROW...

34:16.382 --> 34:18.919
THEY'RE GONNA
PUT US OUT.

34:21.888 --> 34:25.692
OKAY.

34:25.692 --> 34:26.860
[ SNIFFLES ]

34:26.860 --> 34:28.829
SO WHAT,
THAT'S IT?

34:31.364 --> 34:35.902
I COOKED US
A GOOD MEAL.

34:35.902 --> 34:37.037
OH.

34:39.072 --> 34:42.308
MOM,
SAY SOMETHING.

34:42.308 --> 34:45.411
ONE DAY, YOU GONNA LISTEN
TO YOUR MAMA.

34:45.411 --> 34:48.549
BUT UNTIL THEN...

34:48.549 --> 34:51.484
I CAN'T SAY NOTHING.

34:51.484 --> 34:53.920
♪♪♪♪

34:53.920 --> 34:56.056
WE'RE JUST GONNA ENJOY
THIS NIGHT.

34:56.056 --> 34:58.424
♪♪♪♪

34:58.424 --> 35:02.435
♪♪ SHINE ♪♪

35:02.435 --> 35:08.441
♪♪ ON ME ♪♪

35:08.441 --> 35:12.245
♪♪ SHINE ♪♪

35:12.245 --> 35:16.116
♪♪ ON ME ♪♪

35:16.116 --> 35:17.751
[ CRIES ]

35:17.751 --> 35:21.622
♪♪ SHINE ♪♪

35:21.622 --> 35:24.591
♪♪ ON ME ♪♪

35:24.591 --> 35:26.627
♪♪ LET THE LIGHT ♪♪

35:26.627 --> 35:29.129
♪♪ OF THE LIGHTHOUSE ♪♪

35:29.129 --> 35:33.499
♪♪ SHINE DOWN ON ME ♪♪

35:37.137 --> 35:38.739
THANK YOU, LADIES,
FOR COMING.

35:38.739 --> 35:39.973
I REALLY APPRECIATE THIS.

35:39.973 --> 35:42.375
OKAY,
LET'S JUST GET DOWN TO THIS.

35:42.375 --> 35:45.011
YES, LET'S.

35:46.647 --> 35:49.149
JENNIFER,
I DON'T CARE IF YOU GO AFTER ME.

35:49.149 --> 35:50.283
BUT MY SON ‐‐

35:50.283 --> 35:51.585
I GAVE YOUR SON UP.

35:51.585 --> 35:53.620
ALL HE'S DOING
IS TESTIFYING.

35:53.620 --> 35:55.789
BUT HE STILL HAS ACCESS
TO HIS INHERITANCE,

35:55.789 --> 35:57.123
AND THAT
WILL KILL HIM.

35:57.123 --> 35:58.725
THAT IS NOT MY ISSUE.

35:58.725 --> 36:00.133
THAT'S HIS MONEY.

36:01.167 --> 36:02.402
JENNIFER...

36:02.402 --> 36:06.206
I NEED THAT JUDGE
TO RESCIND HIS DECISION

36:06.206 --> 36:08.208
TO ACCESS THAT MONEY.

36:08.208 --> 36:10.343
I CAN'T MAKE IT HAPPEN.

36:10.343 --> 36:12.345
YOU HAVE TO
GO BACK TO HIM.

36:12.345 --> 36:13.514
I WON'T.

36:13.514 --> 36:16.416
JENNIFER, I...

36:16.416 --> 36:18.318
I'M SORRY.

36:18.318 --> 36:20.687
CAN'T YOU AT LEAST
REDUCE IT?

36:20.687 --> 36:22.823
I WILL TALK
TO WYATT

36:22.823 --> 36:25.225
WHEN HE'S ABLE
TO SPEAK.

36:25.225 --> 36:26.527
TALK TO WYATT?

36:26.527 --> 36:29.763
[ SCOFFS ]
HE WON'T GIVE IT UP.

36:29.763 --> 36:32.032
I'M SORRY.

36:32.032 --> 36:34.267
HE WILL KILL HIMSELF
THIS TIME.

36:34.267 --> 36:37.538
I'M SORRY.

36:37.538 --> 36:38.939
SO MY SON'S LIFE?

36:38.939 --> 36:42.208
THAT IS THE CHANCE
YOU ARE WILLING TO TAKE,

36:42.208 --> 36:44.745
ALL BECAUSE YOU AND JIM
HAD SOME KIND OF AFFAIR?

36:44.745 --> 36:45.912
WHAT?

36:45.912 --> 36:47.047
[ SCOFFS ]

36:47.047 --> 36:49.282
DID HE
BREAK YOUR HEART?

36:49.282 --> 36:50.684
[ LAUGHS ]

36:50.684 --> 36:54.555
I NEVER SLEPT
WITH YOUR HUSBAND.

36:54.555 --> 36:56.723
THAT IS LAUGHABLE.

36:56.723 --> 36:59.192
WELL,
HE SAID THAT ‐‐

36:59.192 --> 37:00.426
[ LAUGHS ]

37:00.426 --> 37:01.768
JIM? PLEASE!

37:01.768 --> 37:03.670
NOT ONLY IS THAT...

37:03.670 --> 37:07.807
A COMPLETE LIE,
BUT IT'S ‐‐ IT'S A STRETCH.

37:07.807 --> 37:10.209
DAVID ISN'T,
IS HE?

37:10.209 --> 37:11.578
NO.

37:11.578 --> 37:14.280
DAVID WOULD STRETCH ME.

37:15.314 --> 37:19.485
YOU KNOW,
YOU ARE A VULGAR PIECE OF TRASH.

37:19.485 --> 37:22.022
AREN'T YOU GETTING DIVORCED?

37:23.557 --> 37:27.460
YOU'RE GETTING OFF COURSE,
MISS SALLISON.

37:28.895 --> 37:32.465
NOW, PLEASE...
MY SON.

37:34.601 --> 37:37.403
DO YOU KNOW WHY
I ASKED YOU HERE TODAY?

37:37.403 --> 37:40.273
YES, AND THE ANSWER
IS STILL THE SAME.

37:40.273 --> 37:43.577
I WILL TALK
TO YOUR SON.

37:43.577 --> 37:47.080
HE'LL NEVER
LET YOU DO IT.

37:47.080 --> 37:49.049
WELL,
OKAY THEN.

37:49.049 --> 37:52.519
WE HAVE NOTHING ELSE
TO TALK ABOUT.

37:52.519 --> 37:54.320
WELL, OKAY, THEN.

37:56.122 --> 37:58.124
WHICH BRINGS ME
TO THE OTHER REASON

37:58.124 --> 38:00.460
I'VE ASKED YOU BOTH HERE.

38:00.460 --> 38:03.136
BECAUSE, VERONICA...

38:03.136 --> 38:04.337
HMM?

38:04.337 --> 38:08.141
I'M NOT SURE YOU FULLY KNOW
WHY YOU'RE HERE.

38:08.141 --> 38:09.976
♪♪♪♪

38:09.976 --> 38:13.847
YOU LET A RAPIST
IN THE CELL WITH MY SON.

38:13.847 --> 38:15.348
♪♪♪♪

38:15.348 --> 38:16.717
I DID WHAT?

38:16.717 --> 38:19.019
DON'T DO THAT.
I DID NOT DO THAT.

38:19.019 --> 38:23.824
DO NOT MAKE THE MISTAKE
OF DENYING IT.

38:23.824 --> 38:25.091
I KNOW.

38:26.627 --> 38:28.529
YOU...

38:28.529 --> 38:32.198
ARE HERE
FOR TWO REASONS...

38:32.198 --> 38:34.835
AND TWO REASONS ONLY.

38:34.835 --> 38:36.136
ONE...

38:36.136 --> 38:42.375
IS THAT YOU ARE THE GREATEST
ATTORNEY IN THIS COUNTRY.

38:42.375 --> 38:46.312
I'VE SEEN YOU GET
THE WORST OF THE WORST OFF.

38:46.312 --> 38:48.749
NO ONE IS BETTER.

38:48.749 --> 38:53.086
JIM WAS A FOOL
NOT TO USE YOU.

38:53.086 --> 38:58.892
BUT HE DIDN'T TRUST YOU
BECAUSE OF HIS EGO.

39:01.535 --> 39:03.570
BUT I TRUST YOU.

39:04.871 --> 39:06.707
YOU KNOW WHY?

39:06.707 --> 39:11.177
YOU FEAR NOTHING
AND NO ONE.

39:11.177 --> 39:14.915
YOU'RE LIKE A COCKROACH.

39:14.915 --> 39:17.951
YOU'RE ALWAYS AROUND,
LURKING,

39:17.951 --> 39:21.087
HIDING IN THE DARK.

39:21.087 --> 39:23.957
BUT TODAY,
BITCH...

39:23.957 --> 39:28.494
I'M GONNA TEACH YOU
WHO TO FEAR...

39:28.494 --> 39:30.664
AND HOW TO FEAR.

39:30.664 --> 39:35.001
BECAUSE YOU WILL FEAR ME
FOREVER.

39:35.001 --> 39:36.537
I PROMISE.

39:36.537 --> 39:38.805
♪♪♪♪

39:38.805 --> 39:40.907
THAT'S ONE REASON.

39:40.907 --> 39:42.809
AND THE OTHER...

39:42.809 --> 39:46.513
IS SO
YOU WILL WILLINGLY WITNESS

39:46.513 --> 39:50.617
THE FURY THAT RUNS COLD
IN MY VEINS.

39:50.617 --> 39:53.987
BECAUSE UNLIKE
YOU AND JIM,

39:53.987 --> 39:58.692
I DON'T HIRE PEOPLE
TO DO MY DIRTY WORK.

39:58.692 --> 40:02.335
I DON'T TAKE
THE EASY WAY OUT.

40:02.335 --> 40:05.606
I WALK
IN THE FRONT DOOR.

40:05.606 --> 40:08.008
JENNIFER...

40:09.543 --> 40:12.245
...I'M GOING TO ASK YOU
ONE LAST TIME

40:12.245 --> 40:13.914
TO HELP ME
SAVE MY SON.

40:13.914 --> 40:16.282
♪♪♪♪

40:16.282 --> 40:18.685
LET ME HAVE
HIS INHERITANCE.

40:18.685 --> 40:20.987
NO.

40:22.523 --> 40:26.693
OKAY.

40:26.693 --> 40:27.728
[ GASPS ]

40:27.728 --> 40:30.096
[ SCREAMING ]

40:30.096 --> 40:31.464
♪♪♪♪

40:31.464 --> 40:32.699
[ GASPING ]

40:32.699 --> 40:33.934
BITCH.

40:33.934 --> 40:37.938
♪♪♪♪

40:44.711 --> 40:46.279
[ GASPS, SCREAMS ]

40:46.279 --> 40:48.949
♪♪♪♪

40:48.949 --> 40:51.384
NOW YOUR JOB...

40:51.384 --> 40:53.386
♪♪♪♪

40:53.386 --> 40:56.790
...IS TO GET ME OFF.

40:56.790 --> 41:00.801
♪♪♪♪

41:09.309 --> 41:11.912
[ WHIMPERS ]

41:11.912 --> 41:14.981
♪♪♪♪
